I am having the same problem with version 1.5.8, on simulator and device.

var paint = new SKPaint();
var color = SKColor.Parse("#ff0000");

System.Diagnostics.Debug.WriteLine("CurrentColor: {0}", paint.Color);
System.Diagnostics.Debug.WriteLine("NewColor: {0}", color);
paint.Color = color;
System.Diagnostics.Debug.WriteLine("Result: {0}", paint.Color);

Result:
CurrentColor: #8ef0eee8
NewColor: #ffff0000
Result: #955dfae4
